 Sagoon Inc. Announces Launch of Next-Generation Sagoon Version 2.0 in Kathmandu 
         










    











 






 











 









Sagoon Inc. Announces Launch of Next-Generation Sagoon Version 2.0 in Kathmandu

		  Sagoon Inc., a Washington DC-based start-up, will launch Sagoon version 2.0 on November 8, 2015 in Kathmandu.
		

Nov 02, 2015, 07:00 ET
		  		  					
						 from   Sagoon Inc. 











 
















































 

 




















 


KATHMANDU, Nepal, Nov. 2, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- Sagoon Inc., a Washington DC-based start-up, is proud to announce the launch of Sagoon 2.0 on November 8, 2015, in Kathmandu, Nepal - a country nestled between two large and powerful neighbors, China and India. 
Sagoon's mission is to create a groundbreaking social platform in Asia, capitalizing on its current success and enabling members to simplify their lives while enjoying openness with colleagues, friends and family. 
"Sagoon 2.0 represents a major milestone for Sagoon in its continued efforts to deliver a rewarding experience," says founder Govinda Giri. "Our goal is to take advantage of two huge markets, namely China and India, with a total of one billion Internet users between them. We will launch Sagoon 2.0 in these markets first and then take it global. The next big wave to breathe life into the Internet will be Sagoon. Watch for it!"
Sagoon offers users the opportunity to organize their lives from the time they wake up in the morning until they go to bed at night, enjoying the satisfaction that comes from being well organized and productive. The new version will include: 
- My Day: Offering superior tools to organize users' daily routines, creating schedules, to-do lists and reminders in a quick, simple fashion.
- Open Secrets: Providing a free-for-all platform to disclose information that could be useful to anyone or everyone -- a place to seek and give advice and to help those struggling with their personal relationships, work issues or just life in general. 
- MoodTalk: Livening up chats with fun and customizable moods. Chats are not recorded and vanish after a 24-hour period.
Unlike several other applications, Sagoon 2.0 gives users complete control of their everyday lives, both online and offline. 
Visit blog.sagoon.com for further information, photos and updates about the new version. Sagoon 2.0 is available to users worldwide.
About Sagoon 
Sagoon (sagoon.com) is a social commerce platform with offices located in Washington DC, New Delhi and Kathmandu. There are 30 team members and about 200,000 global users. Sagoon was financed from seed money donated by US-based angel investors.
This press release was issued through 24-7PressRelease.com. For further information, visit http://www.24-7pressrelease.com. 
 
 SOURCE  Sagoon Inc.  

