How do I log into my Sagoon account?

Step 1.  Go to www.sagoon.com and enter one of the following:
                  
Email address: You can log in with your registered email address you have as a Sagoon user.
Username: You can also log in with your username if you entered one while signing up.
Phone number: If you have a mobile phone number confirmed on your account you can enter the same (skip the zeros before the country code)





Step 2.Enter your password
Step 3. Click  Sign In
Step 4. Alternatively, log in using accounts on either Facebook or Google+.






